{"TopicId":170464,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"The Hitchhikers Guide to the Galaxy mod","CreatedByName":"TruPotato","CreatedById":185046,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-04T01:23:32Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"TruPotato","CreatedById":185046,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-04T01:23:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EFirst post.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EHow come there isn\u0027t a Hitchhikers mod for KSP?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\u0022\u003EI\u0027m pretty sure that there\u0027s at least one decent mod creator who also wants this.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont face=\u0022Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\u0022\u003EMaybe something you can attach to a ship that warps\u00A0the craft to a random location when a key is pressed?\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont face=\u0022Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\u0022\u003EProbably something that takes up a lot of fuel when used, to balance it out?\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont face=\u0022Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\u0022\u003E...Hopefully that\u0027s something small and doable, and if not, please don\u0027t make a fuss about how I\u0027ve asked for something too great.\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cfont face=\u0022Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\u0022\u003EThanks! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/font\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-02-04T01:27:57Z\u0022 title=\u00